l-align: -0.838ex; width:28.761ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle x=
_{0}\pm x_{1}=3D(m_{0}\pm m_{1})\times 10^{n_{0}}}"></span>
</p><p>An example:
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
